verbose_text: Since the level of expression of these Rabs were unaltered by the depletion of Rab35 and MICAL-L1 (XREF_FIG, XREF_FIG, XREF_FIG), the Rab8, Rab13, and Rab36 in the Rab35 depleted or MICAL-L1-depleted PC12 cells were likely to have been dispersed from the perinuclear compartments into the cytosol or other membrane compartments.
